HEADWORD: Architeuthis
<hw>Ar`chi*teu"this</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
fr. Gr. pref. <?/ + <?/, <?/, a kind of squid.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A genus of gigantic cephalopods, allied to the squids, found esp.
in the North Atlantic and about New Zealand.</def>⟦br⟧
